Syntax: repair <item>

One of the basic skills all mages learn during their training
is the ability to magically mend some types of equipment.  Mages
have become particularily adept at repairing objects made of
various magical materials and some types of stone.

The appropriate tools must be held and in the room and the item
you wish to repair must be in your inventory in order to repair
it.

Mages can repair equipment made of magical material:

Tools necessary:
 Primary:   runes
 Secondary: energy
 In-room:   pentagram


Mages can repair equipment made of some types of stone:

Tools necessary:
 Primary:   chisel
 Secondary: silicon
 In-room:   pentagram

